{"tid":1467882,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"我老母睇直播見到個大陸比人綁佢咁講","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:40.000Z","uid":262466,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ed24ccad3ff6ee8d7e0ba5b61580b5bdf2faaf8","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />老母<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩圍佢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌咩，一定係大陸狗啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都傻嘅，上次扮完示威者又黎？一定比人捉啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咪係，我本身對大陸公安都半信咋，而家冇得唔信。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D警察入面都有公安啊痴線，有咩理由咁樣？<br />\n<br />\n（見直播綁條友）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />用索帶綁佢囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係啦，唔好比佢走，佢番到大陸D屋企人都見到曬。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁大個仔終於上鏡出名咗次。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />哈哈係囉。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又綁但冇打佢？之前佢D咁嘅福建幫嘅人打人喎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢好彩，我都想打9佢啦cls<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D咁嘅公安打到示威嘅人爆曬血喎，唔打佢真係佢好彩，試下係暗角？我實打佢。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />抵死啦。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我同我老母都唔割</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你地要割？</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">信唔信我鍚曬你地春袋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我真係錫嫁唔好迫我</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"090aa91fd71ea251f49900006e05404d9c144bc3","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:40:50.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60ab01efe648a6076aa268e915520f5996a04c0","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:00.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82686fcaef206dc79bae7fe9ae4ae5bab0d5ea7e","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f14ee17db4015645524fd674604d9f495ae8e9","tid":1467882,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/KviyEOR.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKviyEOR.gif&h=d2c73fea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfca37749bb580e04f327ea66632cd74019b4026","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47bf1ac3378a9a4c972e50de839ab7214b77845","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:00.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3ad8cb2eb558cd57aabe552075abf8cd36ce48","tid":1467882,"uid":262466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:42:10.000Z","msg":"自推十次<img src=\"/ass